00:44:57.480 --> 00:44:59.530
we have an obesity issue,
and a health issue,

00:44:59.530 --> 00:45:00.570
and diabetes issues.

00:45:00.570 --> 00:45:02.440
But it's very real.

00:45:02.440 --> 00:45:07.700
