bifurcation even in our

00:45:11.530 --> 00:45:13.650
community of the haves
and have nots.

00:45:13.650 --> 00:45:17.280
And I think there needs to be
something that addresses that

00:45:17.280 --> 00:45:20.300
gap locally and globally
at the same time.

